{"tid":1047431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大規模監控】外國駭客揭露 具有中國特色的「開放資料」","createTime":"2019-03-05T02:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T08:31:08.000Z","uid":138409,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"033c3bdef786c67b91cf3789d98111fc553ec8b7","tid":1047431,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T02:52:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/g0v.news/photos/a.1828658530736759/2345625005706773/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fg0v.news%2Fphotos%2Fa.1828658530736759%2F2345625005706773%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=a5ba0d6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/g0v.news/photos/a.1828658530736759/2345625005706773/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n具有中國特色的「開放資料」<br />\n<br />\n上次撈出新疆監控資料的駭客 Victor Gevers，這次又有驚人發現。他發現<br />\n<br />\n1. 中國的監控系統搜集來自 QQ、QQ群、ＹＹ、微信、蘋果imessage（疑似，可能來自貴州伺服器）、阿里旺旺的通訊資訊，會記錄包括 <span style=\"color: gold;\">ID、ID 頭像、GPS 位置、 服務商資訊和所有對話內容</span>並傳送到一個超巨大伺服器。<br />\n<br />\n2. 每天約傳送 3.64億個人資料與其對話紀錄。<span style=\"color: orange;\">這些帳號會跟真實身份對照起來並根據省份和城市傳送到當地的警局。</span><br />\n<br />\n3. 中央資料庫傳送到各地警局是系統自動設定，各地警局每天會檢視這些資料並且<span style=\"color: gold;\">手動製作一個新的資料報告。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 大部分的對話紀錄是<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">年輕人的日常對話</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原推文：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/0xDUDE/status/1102303971765641216\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F0xDUDE%2Fstatus%2F1102303971765641216&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=99489de5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F0xDUDE%2Fstatus%2F1102303971765641216&h=e5abcb1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/0xDUDE/status/1102303971765641216</a>"},{"pid":"2ae7ff5ef1f36d47acbbc000eaf5590c384d577c","tid":1047431,"uid":100131,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:02:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁撚多資料/對話點手動去執？"},{"pid":"596a501bc8820517b32e36ff53ec9faf8be7d853","tid":1047431,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":29,"score":-29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:07:10.000Z","msg":"<code>Xboxone Contana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"3580a81842f7ea94db4ace61476a6a977adf6a77","tid":1047431,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T04:51:58.000Z","msg":"睇嚟駭客都可以做好事"},{"pid":"598a35efad1366752ddbe0edf38eb5208917e2b5","tid":1047431,"uid":4208,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"3580a81842f7ea94db4ace61476a6a977adf6a77","tid":1047431,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T04:51:58.000Z","msg":"睇嚟駭客都可以做好事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T04:53:59.000Z","msg":"黑客本身就有分好同壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61af36315a5134dd1063c0c51fc1a04b7c1d93cf","tid":1047431,"uid":34010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T04:54:10.000Z","msg":"蘋果imessage<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dfe6617ec4b8933a54755e881a7eb39fba932ab","tid":1047431,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"598a35efad1366752ddbe0edf38eb5208917e2b5","tid":1047431,"uid":4208,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"3580a81842f7ea94db4ace61476a6a977adf6a77","tid":1047431,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T04:51:58.000Z","msg":"睇嚟駭客都可以做好事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T04:53:59.000Z","msg":"黑客本身就有分好同壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T04:56:01.000Z","msg":"咁好嗰隻包唔包hack入去政府機構爆人大鑊？