\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T05:17:45.000Z","msg":"官方答案，只係中國大陸用貴州server<br />\n不過都係講個信字<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n進一步瞭解中國的 iCloud 服務<br />\n瞭解中國 iCloud 服務的異動。<br />\n<br />\n中國大陸的 iCloud 服務，現由中國網路服務公司雲上貴州大數據產業發展有限公司（雲上貴州）負責營運。這使我們能持續改善在中國的 iCloud 服務，並遵循當地法規。<br />\niCloud 服務以及所有儲存於 iCloud 的資料，包含照片、影片、文件以及備份，均將受到新 iCloud（由雲上貴州營運）條款和條件的約束。<br />\n如果您不是現居於中國大陸的中國公民，您可以在設定中編輯您 Apple ID 的國家或地區，來顯示您目前所在的國家或地區，以繼續使用適用於目前 Apple 條款和條件的 iCloud 服務。<br />\n發佈日期： 2018年3月22日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/HT208351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fzh-tw%2FHT208351&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=4a175362\" target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/HT208351</a>"},{"pid":"a393b8d4a22cfdd217dd775f8ead0529cdc2ead6","tid":1047431,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T05:17:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/0xDUDE/status/1101909112131080192\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F0xDUDE%2Fstatus%2F1101909112131080192&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=39d8b9fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F0xDUDE%2Fstatus%2F1101909112131080192&h=068fb979\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/0xDUDE/status/1101909112131080192</a>"},{"pid":"2f0561a52e1d6da0b72c9d98640b792732a473d6","tid":1047431,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T05:28:33.000Z","msg":"中國軟件,駁上網一刻所有野已經gpl<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37bb1f22c47f475cbe7fbb820f322947a8e30af","tid":1047431,"uid":20449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T05:34:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0117965ac8834eaa46dcdd0ba274a45ceae768fa","tid":1047431,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T05:34:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76aca135767dc14383